Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:08.62,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,He’s not a careless person, so he must have been looking for a time to come and talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:14.22,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I just didn’t notice him because I’ve been so saturated with thinking about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:18.21,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But... I’ve been avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:21.68,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,How stupid.
