Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:37.09,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I can’t give up until I hear it from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:38.75,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It’s all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:46.06,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But if this is all just a rumor, I couldn’t say how happy I would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.86,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I’m sad...Takeshi-san.
